HEADWORD: Agrostis
<hw>A*gros"tis</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr. Gr.
<?/.]</ety> <def>A genus of grasses, including species called in common
language <xex>bent grass</xex>. Some of them, as redtop (<spn>Agrostis
vulgaris</spn>), are valuable pasture grasses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

